    </solution>
    </exercise>
        <exercise id="fs-id2000830" type="problems-exercises"><problem id="fs-id1997560">    <para id="import-auto-id3110312">What frequency sound has a 0.10-m wavelength when the speed of sound is 340 m/s?</para>
    </problem></exercise>
    <exercise id="fs-id3043771" type="problems-exercises"><problem id="fs-id1945477">    <para id="import-auto-id1870708">Calculate the speed of sound on a day when a 1500 Hz frequency has a wavelength of 0.221 m.</para>
